"    Print",
"   </a>",
"   <a class=\"etacLink\" href=\"#\">",
"    <img alt=\"Email graphic(s)\" src=\"./../images/icn_email.myextg\" title=\"Email graphic(s)\"/>",
"   </a>",
"   <a class=\"icontxt textLink etacLink\" href=\"#\" title=\"Email graphic(s)\">",
"    Email",
"   </a>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Disseminated granuloma annulare",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 432px; height: 376px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    This 55 year-old patient presented with disseminated granuloma annulare in a brightly erythematous annular and arcuate pattern demonstrating complete central clearing. Scores of similar lesions were present on the trunk and extremities sparing the face, palms, and soles.",
